her family's meals.

16:26.819 --> 16:28.412
- Hey, I'm sorry I'm late,
you know? -Arthur.

16:28.554 --> 16:31.216
I just renewed
my "liberry" card.

16:32.758 --> 16:34.749
Oh. Conference time.

16:34.894 --> 16:37.795
Uh, couldn't it wait
a second, Fonz? Uh...

16:37.930 --> 16:41.093
Somebody's aunt is on thin ice.

16:42.134 --> 16:43.101
- Aunt?
-(Fonzie snaps fingers)

16:43.236 --> 16:45.671
Uh, conference time.

16:45.805 --> 16:49.207
You remember a letter that
you wrote to a Troubled Twosome?

16:49.342 --> 16:51.970
Troubled Twosome.
Uh... oh, yeah, yeah,

16:52.111 --> 16:53.670
uh, the husband and the wife.

16:53.813 --> 16:55.372
- No husband, no wife.
- No?

16:55.515 --> 16:56.607
No.

16:56.749 --> 16:58.911
Try a Ralph and a Potsie.

16:59.051 --> 17:00.610
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

17:00.753 --> 17:02.517
No. How bad is it?

17:02.655 --> 17:03.781
- Let's put it this way.
- Yeah?

17:03.923 --> 17:05.288
You're a home wrecker.

17:07.727 --> 17:10.252
Will you clue me in
on what we're having over there?

17:10.396 --> 17:11.693
- Apple surprise.
- What is it?

17:11.830 --> 17:12.763
You got me.

17:12.898 --> 17:14.765
- Mother Kelp.
- That's it, Fonz.

17:14.901 --> 17:16.630
All right,
you're having two of 'em.

17:16.769 --> 17:18.362
I'm only having one.

17:18.503 --> 17:20.165
You're having two of 'em.

17:20.306 --> 17:22.832
Two.

17:22.974 --> 17:26.741
(chuckles): Hey-hey,
how are you? That's great.

17:26.878 --> 17:29.211
Apple surprise!

17:35.187 --> 17:38.384
<i>II</i>

17:41.794 --> 17:43.592
You don't let up, Pots,
