17:43.729 --> 17:45.663
Wait a minute,
you don't let up over and ov...

17:45.798 --> 17:47.197
Wait a minute.
You can't come in.

17:47.333 --> 17:48.801
The door's
on my side of the room.

17:48.935 --> 17:51.427
So what? I traded you one shower
for one coming in the door.

17:51.571 --> 17:52.834
And you used it up this morning.

17:52.972 --> 17:55.703
What are you... Malph,
you better not close that...

