22:49.268 --> 22:51.532
- Called communication.
- The man is right.

22:51.670 --> 22:54.105
I mean, Aunt Fanny
couldn't say it any better.

22:54.240 --> 22:56.106
What's the second choice?

22:56.242 --> 22:58.370
- Don't ask.
- Well...

22:58.510 --> 23:00.877
